<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15108</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那是美罗城繁忙的一天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>人们在路上匆匆行走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>23117</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>西街上挤满了汽车和公交车。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>23118</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轰隆！轰隆！大地突然震动起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29409</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>32885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“地震了！”一个女人喊道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>32886</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36915</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一道巨大的影子遮住了街道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36916</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40392</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都抬头看。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40393</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43802</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个男人咽了一口口水。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那......那是什么？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克有一只新飞盘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>58508</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西和她的朋友们正在玛拉家的后院里玩儿飞盘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>58509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61097</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗨，玛拉，接着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61098</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克大声叫道，把飞盘扔了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71559</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉快速地跑过去接它。“接住了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71560</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“把它扔过来！”特勒尔叫道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>80494</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔接住飞盘后，扔向罗西。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>80495</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西接住后又扔给杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87432</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克拿着飞盘扇风。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87433</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90744</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天太热了。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90745</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要是能去游泳就好了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我让妈妈带我们去市区游泳馆了。”玛拉说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103681</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不过，她今天事儿太多了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103682</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110934</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“今天不能去新开的水上乐园，真是太可惜了。”特勒尔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110935</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那里有水滑梯，还有很棒的人工造浪机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118936</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>比游泳馆好多了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118937</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124935</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>玛拉耸耸肩。“热，我们也没办法。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124936</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们还是接着玩儿飞盘吧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134185</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这里，罗西，接着！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134186</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141434</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西接住了飞盘，然后又把它扔向了特勒尔。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>146184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呀！对不起，特勒尔！”她叫道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>146185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148580</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚才我扔得不好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148581</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151192</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔去追飞盘。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151193</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157669</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不过，飞盘在他抓住之前，已经飞过栅栏了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157670</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>162490</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>飞盘掉进了邻居家的后院里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>162491</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>166328</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我的新飞盘！”杰克说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>166329</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171143</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我去捡。”特勒尔说。他翻过栅栏。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171144</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>175809</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>几分钟以后，特勒尔带着飞盘回来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>175810</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179511</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>汗从他的额头上流下来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179512</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>183716</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我现在好热啊。”他抱怨道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>183717</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“要是火箭女孩儿在这里就好了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187110</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>194468</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她也许可以改变天气——下雨或者下雪，让我们凉快凉快。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>194469</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200718</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西大笑起来。“对，火箭女孩儿肯定能做到。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200719</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>205717</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你也这么认为吗？”特勒尔充满希望地看着她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>205718</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>210753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。”罗西说，“火箭女孩儿是很强大，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>210754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213385</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是她不能改变天气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213386</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>218134</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>再说，火箭女孩儿有更重要的事情要做。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>218135</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220475</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你说得对，罗西。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220476</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225644</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>特勒尔皱着眉头，把飞盘扔给杰克。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225645</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>230296</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>就在这时，罗西的手表响了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>230297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>234218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很快就回来。”罗西说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>234219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>罗西很快地跑进玛拉家里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240872</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她马上打开手表。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240873</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243786</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>布洛姆市长的脸出现了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243787</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246423</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看上去很担心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“布洛姆市长。”罗西说，“您有什么事吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250667</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255283</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们需要你的帮助，火箭女孩儿。”市长说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255284</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>259535</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“一只巨大的怪物正在毁灭美罗城。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>259536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>266753</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别担心，市长！”罗西说，“我很快就到！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>